page.title: 20THE BROWNIES (cont.)
page.content: A light brown dress,dark brown belt and hat and a yellow tie with a silver badge. In our brownie pocket we should have a tissue, 10p for the phone, a pen, a note book or paper, a plaster, and the great big brownie smile. We are called the 2nd Narborough brownie pack.Our pack is led by three women, whom we call BROWN OWL, ROBIN and WREN.In our pack we have four different groups called sixes,known as Sprites,Imps,Elves and Kelpies.There are many different names for sixes but we have only these.
